Uniform Distribution
The probability density function of a variable uniformly distributed between 0 and 2 is
\[\begin{align*}
    f(x) =
        \begin{cases}
        \dfrac{1}{2} & \text{if } 0 \leq x \leq 2 \\
        0   & \text{otherwise }
        \end{cases}
\end{align*}\]

